{% if section.settings.show_banner %}
  <section class="page-header about-area-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-12 col-md-5">
          <div class="banner-about-img">
            <img src="{{ section.settings.banner_image | image_url }}" alt="About Image">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-12 col-md-7">
          <div class="page-header-content">
            <h1 class="title">{{ section.settings.banner_heading }}</h1>
            <h4 class="sub-title">{{ section.settings.banner_subheading }}</h4>
            <div class="hero-btn-wrap">
              <a href="{{ section.settings.banner_button_link }}" class="ed-primary-btn">
                {{ section.settings.banner_button_text }}
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endif %}

{% if section.settings.show_brand_story %}
  <section class="brand-story-area">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center promise-area text-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12 col-md-12 mb-4">
          <div class="promise-content">
            <div class="section-heading mb-40">
              <h2>Brand Story</h2>
              <h4 class="sub-title">We’re Men. And We Care.</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-brand-area-left-auto">
      <div class="brand-story-text">
        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="section-heading mb-40">
            <h3>Just Like You.</h3>
            <p class="mt-20">Hey, we’re just like you — men who never gave skincare a second thought until one day, it started to show. Tired eyes. Dry skin. Razor burns that felt like battles lost. 
              <br />Back in 2012, our founder stood in the grooming aisle, overwhelmed by labels that promised too much and delivered too little. Shelves full of floral-scented creams and 12-step routines… for women. But for men? A lonely face wash and maybe an all-in-one that smelt like dish soap. 
              <br />That’s when a thought hit — why should skincare feel like a chore for men? 
              <br />Why can’t it be smart, no-fuss, and actually made for our skin? 
              <br />The first step was C-mens — a humble experiment that opened the door. The response? 
              <br /> Encouraging. But we knew men deserved more than a line of products. They deserved a brand that truly understood their lifestyle, their skin, and their silence. And so, Mensense was born. 
              <br />We created a skincare system that’s direct, effective, and designed to work harder, not longer. 
              <br />No 20-minute routines. Just real results, backed by science and sensibility. 
              <br />Because let’s face it — we don’t want clutter. We want confidence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-story-right-img">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0949/0975/9774/files/about-brand-right1.png?v=1756547473" alt="brand story">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endif %}

{% if section.settings.show_vision_mission %}
