    <div class="container">
      <div class="row-are">
        <div class="mission-image">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0949/0975/9774/files/mission-img.jpg?v=1756550839" alt="Skincare Dropper">
        </div>
        <div class="mission-text">
          <div class="about-content">
            <div class="section-heading mb-40">
              <h2>Our Vision</h2>
              <p>Back in 2012, men’s skincare in India was an afterthought. Our founder saw the gap and built C-mens — a brand that started the conversation. Mensense takes it further, with superior ingredients, international standards, and a sharp focus on what men actually need.</p>
              <p>We’re here to make skincare simple, effective, and unapologetically masculine.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row-are">
        <div class="mission-text vision-text">
          <div class="about-content">
            <div class="section-heading mb-40">
              <h2>Our Vision</h2>
              <p>Back in 2012, men’s skincare in India was an afterthought. Our founder saw the gap and built C-mens — a brand that started the conversation. Mensense takes it further, with superior ingredients, international standards, and a sharp focus on what men actually need.</p>
              <p>We’re here to make skincare simple, effective, and unapologetically masculine.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-image">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0949/0975/9774/files/vision-img.jpg?v=1756550839" alt="Skincare Dropper">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
